[SN]TITLE[SN]
What it's like to go three days without technology

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
As part of our new special, 'Is Tech taking Over?', we've been looking into how much we use technology, and what impact it's having on our lives.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
23 March 2016 Last updated at 07:01 GMT
Technology is everywhere, we use it to chat to our friends, play games and keep up to date with what's going on in the world.
We set a special challenge for a group of 11-12 year olds to find out whether they could cope with restrictions to their technology use over three days.
Here's how they got on.
